; L5: One box, three jobs (FIXED: v-shape path ensures ENERGY is reachable)
; Player at (1,3), Box at (3,4), Button at (5,3), Door at (6,3),
;   Enemy at (5,5), Socket at (7,3), Goal at (8,3)
;
; Box orientation trace (initial: T=NORMAL_A, F=HEAVY):
;   R1: box (4,4), top=IMPACT
;   R2: box (5,4), top=NORMAL   → button cell (5,3) reached by walking, not box
;   D1: box (5,5), top=HEAVY    → enemy at (5,5) DEFEATED!
;   R1: box (6,5), top=IMPACT
;   R2: box (7,5), top=NORMAL
;   U1: box (7,4), top=ENERGY
;   U2: box (7,3), top=ENERGY   → socket activated!
;
; Player path: walk right → push box R2 → walk up-right → push box D1 → push R2 U2 → walk to goal

